trans-unit.source: Represents an expression used as a method invoke parameter along with a reference direction indicator.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et uttrykk som brukes som en metode aktivere parameteren sammen med en referanse retningen indikator.

trans-unit.source: CodeDirectionExpression can represent a parameter passed to a method and the reference direction of the parameter.
trans-unit.target: CodeDirectionExpression kan representere en parameter som er sendt til en metode og referanse retningen for parameteren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDirectionExpression.Expression%2A> property indicates the expression to qualify with a direction.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDirectionExpression.Expression%2A>egenskapen angir uttrykket til å kvalifisere uten en retning.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDirectionExpression.Expression%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDirectionExpression.Direction%2A> property indicates the direction of the parameter using one of the <xref:System.CodeDom.FieldDirection> enumeration values.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDirectionExpression.Direction%2A>egenskapen angir retningen for parameteren for den <xref:System.CodeDom.FieldDirection>nummereringsverdier.</xref:System.CodeDom.FieldDirection> </xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDirectionExpression.Direction%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > CodeDirectionExpression is intended to be used as a method invoke parameter, and should not be used when declaring methods.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > CodeDirectionExpression skal brukes som en metode aktivere parameteren, og bør ikke bli brukt når deklarerer metoder.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeDirectionExpression"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeDirectionExpression"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeDirectionExpression"></xref> class using the specified field direction and expression.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeDirectionExpression"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av angitt felt retningen og uttrykk.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.FieldDirection"></xref> that indicates the field direction of the expression.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.FieldDirection"> </xref> som angir feltet sorteringsretningen uttrykket.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"></xref> that indicates the code expression to represent.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"> </xref> som angir code-uttrykket til å representere.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the field direction for this direction expression.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir feltet retningen for dette retningen-uttrykket.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.FieldDirection"></xref> that indicates the field direction for this direction expression.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.FieldDirection"> </xref> som angir feltet retningen for dette retningen-uttrykket.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the code expression to represent.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir code-uttrykket til å representere.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"></xref> that indicates the expression to represent.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"> </xref> som angir uttrykket som representerer.
